title: Post Game: For Democrats, the number is moving
description: Sen. Cory Booker talks to Chuck Todd about negotiations between centrist and progressive Democrats. DHS Sec. Mayorkas defends efforts to send migrants back to Haiti. Allie Sandza talks to Chuck about what went into this week’s broadcast of Meet the Press.
